
----> Quoted and Reported Speech

	Quoted Speech: Statements
		She said, "I like the class"
		She said, "I'm having a lot of fun"
		She said, "I just saw him"
		She said, "I have seen the movie"
		She said, "I am going to finish it"
		She said, "I will study by myself"
		She said, "I may take the train"
		She said, "I can do it"
		She said, "I should call my mom"
		
	Quoted Speech: Yes/No Questions	
		He asked, "Do you like music?"
		He asked, "Teressa, Can you drive?"
		
	Quoted Speech: Information Questions
		I asked, "Where do you live, Maria?"
		I asked, "Maria, How are your parents?"
